name: AAST363
title: Filipino American History and Biography
description: Cross-listed with: AMST323. Credit only granted for: AAST363, AMST323, AAST398D, or AMST328J. Formerly: AAST398D. Focus is placed on Filipino American experiences with an emphasis on identity, community building and organizing to influence public policy We will cover pertinent events from the US and Philippine history in order to understand the impact of colonialism, migration, immigration and assimilation on Filipino Americans.
